long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly extract Wellfound jobs data from the search page to a Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML file. Perfect for job seekers, recruiters, and market analysts.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Go to the Wellfound jobs search page.
2️⃣ Perform a search, then click the "Start" button on extension popup.
3️⃣ Choose to download from the data scraping pop-up or the task list on extension.

🌳 What wellfound jobs data can I extract using this tool?
Like badges, companySize, highConcept, jobAutoPosted, jobCompensation, jobDescription, jobType, jobLiveStartAt, jobLocationNames, jobPrimaryRoleTitle, jobRemote, jobSlug, jobTitle, jobId, jobIsBookmarked, jobUrl, companyId, companyLogoUrl, companyName, companyUrl and so on.

Note: This extension is an independent creation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by facebook❗️🔒
